<h2>Single Statement Stages of Change Questionnaire</h2>
<p><i>These next questions help us better understand the way you view your amputation-related problems. Each statement describes how you may feel about these particular problems. After I read the statement, please tell me if you agree or disagree with the statement. Okay?</i></p>

<table>
	<tr>
		<th>Question</th>
		<th>Response</th>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td>1. There is nothing I can do to manage my amputation-related problems without medication or other medical intervention.</td>
		<td><%= select(:followup6month, :fu6month_soc_1,
			[["",nil],
			["Strongly Disagree",1],
			["Disagree",2],
			["Undecided or Unsure",3],
			["Agree",4],
			["Strongly Disagree",5]]) %>
		</td>
	</tr>

	<tr>
		<td>2. I'm not sure whether I should rely on medical solutions for my amputation-related problems, or should realize that I need to manage the problems.</td>
