			["Strongly Disagree",1],
			["Disagree",2],
			["Undecided or Unsure",3],
			["Agree",4],
			["Strongly Disagree",5]]) %>
		</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td>3. While my doctor can help, managing my amputation-related problems is up to me, and I am ready to begin to learn to deal with it.</td>
